posting_body: ['SPECTACULAR Floor to Ceiling Window Unit in PRIME Financial District!!', 'To view, call or text Sarah Sachs at (646) 248-6609', 'Listing ID #: 138527', 'Price: $4,609', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Bedrooms: Studio', 'Bathrooms: 1.0', 'Building Amenities', 'Doorman', 'Elevator', 'Health Club', 'Subway', 'New Construction', 'Laundry', 'Bicycle Room', 'Storage', 'Nursery', 'Lounge', 'Valet', 'Roof Deck', 'Wheelchair Access', 'WiFi', 'Common Outdoor Space', 'Receiving Room', 'Business Center', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Washer', 'Hardwood', 'High Ceilings', 'Light', 'Laundry In Unit', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'To view, call or text Sarah Sachs at (646) 248-6609', 'This GORGEOUS 1 bed 1 bath features floor to ceiling windows overlooking beautiful Manhattan, oak flooring, smart technology for temperature control, blizzard-white quartz countertops, dishwasher, and in unit laundry.', 'Building amenities include a 24 hr doorman, 2 lounges, fitness club, and much more!', 'Located close by Fulton St station with over 6 different train lines and buses.', 'Also by many different restaurants and shops, including Brookfield Place and the Oculus!', 'Sarah Sachs', 'Phone: (646) 248-6609', 'Email:', 'New York Living Solutions - Keller Williams New York City \xa0 (646) 248-6609', 'POSTED BY REALTYMX™', 'To view, call or text Sarah Sachs at (646) 248-6609']
